_refine.details                                  
;HYDROGENS HAVE BEEN ADDED IN THE RIDING POSITIONS. 
THE DATA ARE HIGHLY ANISOTROPIC.
THERE ARE UNMODELLED REGIONS FOR C212-213, C359-363, C372, C423-427, 
 D233, D361-364, D425-427 and D430-432. THE LIGAND MOLECULES IN THE PROTEIN ACTIVE SITES ARE MODELLED AS FOLLOWS: CHAIN A, IN 2 CONFORMATIONS AT OCCUPANCIES 0.6/0.4, CHAIN B, IN 1 CONFORMATION, CHAIN C, WITH THE CARBA-CYCLOPHELLITOL AND AMIDE GROUPS AT OCCUPANCY 1, AND AZIDOBUTYL GROUP AT OCCUPANCY 0.5, CHAIN D, WITH ONLY THE CARBA-CYCLOPHELLITOL AND AMIDE MOIETIES PRESENT, AT OCCUPANCY 1.
;
